### Login
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@assetflow.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### Current User
GET http://localhost:5000/api/auth/me

###

### Logout
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/logout

### Departments
GET http://localhost:5000/api/departments?page=1&limit=10&search=IT

### Assets
GET http://localhost:5000/api/assets?page=1&limit=10&search=LAP&status=AVAILABLE

### Users
GET http://localhost:5000/api/users?page=1&limit=10&role=EMPLOYEE
